sync::nonpoison::mutex::Mutex::<T>::new.doc:
Creates a new mutex in an unlocked state ready for use.

# Examples

```
#![feature(nonpoison_mutex)]

use std::sync::nonpoison::Mutex;

let mutex = Mutex::new(0);
```

